Package com.poesys.db.dao.ddl

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IExecuteSql
    An interface for Command-pattern data access objects (DAOs) that execute a SQL DDL statement.
    ISql
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an ISql object to build a SQL DDL statement, a simple SQL statement that has no parameters and retrieves no data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecuteSql
    An implementation of the ISql interface that executes the SQL statement on demand.
    TruncateTableSql
    A test implementation of the ISql interface that contains a generic TRUNCATE statement.
